  "instructions": [
    "Preheat sous-vide machine to 130°F (54°C).",
    "Season the cod fillet with salt, Jamaican seasoning, and mustard powder.",
    "Place the fish in a sous-vide bag and seal.",
    "Cook the fish for 1 hour 30 minutes.",
    "While the fish is cooking, combine rice flour, all-purpose flour, and salt in a bowl.",
    "Add water to the bowl and mix until a smooth batter forms.",
    "Heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "Drop the batter by tablespoonfuls onto the skillet and cook until bubbles appear on the surface.",
    "Flip the pancakes and cook for another 2-3 minutes.",
    "Serve the pancakes with cooked fish, sour cream, chopped green onions, and lemon wedges."
  ],
